</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Serbitar - there is no specialization check. Specialization is a 100% of the time effect. Always has been. Probably always will be. The savings is the same on each and every cast. The savings is a flat rate based on your skill - 10% at 200, 2.5% at 50.<blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Having SCM3 adds 10% manna preservation on your specialization (for 20% total), and gives you the full 20% manna preservation on non specialized skills?<hr size="1" /></blockquote>1st half - yes, 2nd half no.<br />
<br />
With SCM 3 you get ~20% savings on your primary spcialization.<br />
<br />
Spec 50 gives a 2.5% savings, which when comined with SCM3 gives ~12.5% on your non-primary spec spells.</p>
	
	
	
