	<p>My little SCM test -<br />
<br />
I was saving AAs for SCM.  I had 11 AA saved one day and was close to my 12th.  I stopped the pulls and cast MGB Khuras (don't have Fo7) when I was at 100% mana.  That used 51% of my mana leaving me at 49%.  Not too long later I got my 12th point and went from no points spent into SCM to SCM3.  When MGB popped later I cast MGB Khuras again.  That used 44% of my mana leaving me at 56%.<br />
<br />
I don't know what my exact WIS was, but I had on the same gear and KEI both times.<br />
<br />
Interpret what you will from that info.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
