	<p>The Mage Compendium (mage boards) ran a whole slew of tests over a year ago. With and without packet sniffers. After parsing, sniffing, ect, SCM 3 is a flat 10%. Period. The exact same thing the wiz board came up with.<br />
<br />
SCM is NOT random, there is no check. Its a flat 10%. Search the wiz and mage boards for hundreds of posts on this.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
